gin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n        <tr style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">\r\n            <td width=\"117\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Fak&uuml;lte/SHMYO</strong></td>\r\n            <td width=\"77\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Unvan</strong></td>\r\n            <td width=\"141\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Anabilim Dalı/B&ouml;l&uuml;m/Program</strong></td>\r\n            <td width=\"50\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Kadro Sayısı</strong></td>\r\n            <td width=\"279\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">A&ccedil;ıklama</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; background: rgb(245, 245, 245);\">\r\n            <td width=\"117\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Sağlık Bilimleri</td>\r\n            <td width=\"77\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Profes&ouml;r</td>\r\n            <td width=\"141\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Hemşirelik</td>\r\n            <td width=\"50\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">1</td>\r\n            <td width=\"279\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Psikiyatri Hemşireliği programında doktora yapmış olmak. Ruh sağlığı, psikoonkoloji, danışmanlık, sağlık alanında temel kavramlar, psikososyal hemşirelik, empati, iletişim becerileri, madde bağımlılığı, &ouml;l&uuml;m ve &ouml;tenazi konularında bilimsel &ccedil;alışmaları olmak.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">\r\n            <td width=\"117\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Sağlık Bilimleri</td>\r\n            <td width=\"77\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Profes&ouml;r</td>\r\n            <td width=\"141\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Hemşirelik</td>\r\n            <td width=\"50\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">1</td>\r\n            <td width=\"279\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Doğum ve kadın hastalıkları hemşireliği programında doktora yapmış olmak. Cinsel sağlıkla ilgili eğitim modelleri ve &ouml;l&ccedil;me aracı geliştirme konusunda &ccedil;alışmaları olmak.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; background: rgb(245, 245, 245);\">\r\n            <td width=\"117\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Tıp Fak&uuml;ltesi</td>\r\n            <td width=\"77\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Dr. &Ouml;ğr. &Uuml;yesi</td>\r\n            <td width=\"141\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Tıbbi Biyoloji</td>\r\n            <td width=\"50\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">1</td>\r\n            <td width=\"279\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">T&uuml;m&ouml;r biyolojisi ve imm&uuml;nolojisi programında&nbsp;doktora yapmış olmak. Kemokinlerden t&uuml;revlenmiş k&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k peptit molek&uuml;lleri ile &ccedil;alışmış olmak, Deney hayvanları kanser modellerinin imm&uuml;n mod&uuml;lat&ouml;r etkileri hakkında &ccedil;alışmaları olmak.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">\r\n            <td width=\"117\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Tıp Fak&uuml;ltesi</td>\r\n            <td width=\"77\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Dr. &Ouml;ğr. &Uuml;yesi</td>\r\n            <td width=\"141\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Tıbbi Mikrobiyoloji</td>\r\n            <td width=\"50\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">1</td>\r\n            <td width=\"279\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Tıp Fak&uuml;ltesi Tıbbi Mikrobiyoloji Anabilim Dalında doktora yapmış olmak. Herpes simplex vir&uuml;s tip 1 viral proteinleri ile y&uuml;kl&uuml; dendritik h&uuml;creler &uuml;zerinde ve melanoma gen biyobelirte&ccedil;leri &uuml;zerinde &ccedil;alışmaları olmak. Doktora sonrası en az beş yıl deneyimli olmak.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; background: rgb(245, 245, 245);\">\r\n            <td width=\"117\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Spor Bilimleri Fak&uuml;ltesi</td>\r\n            <td width=\"77\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">&Ouml;ğretim G&ouml;revlisi</td>\r\n            <td width=\"141\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Antren&ouml;rl&uuml;k Eğitimi</td>\r\n            <td width=\"50\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">1</td>\r\n            <td width=\"279\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1vw 0.75vw; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: auto !important;\">Beden Eğitimi ve Spor Alanında doktora yapıyor olmak, 3. kademe y&uuml;zme, fitness, muaythai antren&ouml;rl&uuml;k belgesine sahip olmak.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"outline: none; margin: 1vw 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 77, 79); font-family: Gotham-Book; font-size: 16.896px;\">&nbsp;</p>', '2019-03-05'),
